Marcel von Aulock has resigned as executive director of Tsogo Sun effective 1 June 2017 and from his employment with the hospitality group with effect from 30 June 2017. Von Aulock has served in various capacities in the management of Tsogo Sun for some 18 years and Chief Executive Officer for the last six years. Jacques Booysen will replace von Aulock as Chief Executive Officer with effect from 1 July 2017. Booysen has been with the group for ten years. For the past six years he attended directors’ meetings as an invitee as head of the group’s gaming division and in that capacity has long been von Aulock’s natural successor.